channel.title: For Starters — Everyone on the forum is invited! (Project, collab)
channel.description:
So, @Mr_Mooo and I, have started on this idea/project, where users with the subscription use only the **demo sounds**, and focus on one individual aspect of Auxy (i.e: Volume, reverb, highpass, etc), We already have overall, and highpass.... Anybody willing to join?
https://app.auxy.co/projects/FzsTkUNmQEHIxCX8QCrOJw== =
Osharu Pérez — Overall (https://app.auxy.co/projects/0Rl9C8EoXA_r0KC8LFAtJw==) Mr_Mooo — Highpass (https://app.auxy.co/projects/Pl5Nvsvkrkb5rxSEeasZCw==) Sapphire — Volume (https://app.auxy.co/projects/t0OdBA5qQD9wrvWgOC1ZNQ==) Anirudh Khanna — Lowpass (https://app.auxy.co/projects/IHPdt-bQDnyTeH2Q1CMmiQ==) E|1011 — Tone (https://app.auxy.co/projects/p1USwX4PVSWVl8JwaRJ07A==) Peløton — Shape R-JRDN — Reverb ? — Delay ? — Ducker ? — Pan
